('The Importance of Financial Planning for an Import Project: Accounting for Hidden Costs', 'en', 'financial-planning-import-project', 'Financial planning must include all costs, including product price, shipping, insurance, customs clearance, taxes, and storage fees. New importers often overlook hidden costs such as bank transfer fees or delay charges. A detailed budget must be prepared to avoid surprises [22].', 'Financial planning must include all costs, including product price, shipping, insurance, customs clearance, taxes, and storage fees. New importers oft...', 1, 'Financial Security', 'Financial Planning,Hidden Costs,Budget,Taxes', 0, 1),
